name: Teaser NFT - Reveal Coming Soon
description: REVEAL COMING SOON - Secret society of owlz is a collection of 8,888 unique Owl NFTs — unique digital collectibles living on the Ethereum blockchain. Each Owl will be a playable character for our upcoming NFT-Game 'Owlz Hotel'. Owlz Hotel is an online vintage pixel-art style virtual community where you can make friends, chat, build rooms, design + play games and so much more! Almost anything is possible in this strange place full of awesome people… https://www.secretsocietyofowlz.io for more details.
